Name: Unlimited Fight
About the game: Unlimited Fight is born out of what is a new story created by the enthusiasm of young fighting game lovers. Become a street fighter, a ninja, a soldier, a muay thai fighter, a wrestler, and more in this incredible world. Try one of these fighting styles and enter the Unlimited Fighting tournament one of the iconic characters, each with a different motivation to participate in that tournament, and face friends locally.
